title: 33 Of The Cutest Accessories You've Ever Seen
text:

Zoë Burnett / BuzzFeed We hope you love the products we recommend! Just so you know, BuzzFeed may collect a share of sales from the links on this page.
ID: 10313413 1. A dainty Princess Leia necklace to commemorate a lady who was actually tough as hell. thinkgeek.com
thinkgeek.com
Get it from Think Geek for $17.99 .
ID: 10312555 2. A schoolbus of Hello Kitty collector pins that will brighten your textbook-filled, study-marathoning days. sanrio.com
sanrio.com
 Hello Kitty predicts many A’s in your future.
Get the set from Sanrio for $39 .
ID: 10293308 3. A delightful tote that’ll make you wish you could eat tacos in space. View this image ›
forever21.com Step 1: become an astronaut. Step 2: bring tacos aboard your next mission.
Get it from Forever 21 for $1.90 .
If your taste buds prefer Chinese takeout and fortune cookies, there’s a tote for those too.
ID: 10306212 4. Darling socks that will transform your feet into Disney princesses. View this image ›
amazon.com No bippity, boppity, or boo required.
Get five pairs from Amazon for $14.88 .
ID: 10293793 5. A pair of kittens with nothing better to do than to hang onto your earlobes. View this image ›
amazon.com Get them from Amazon for $18.50 .
ID: 10293709 6. A steaming catpuccino for a double dose of caffeine and cuteness. View this image ›
etsy.com Brb, melting into a coffee puddle.
Get the pin from LindaPanda on Etsy for $12 .
Too busy to sit in a café? Here’s a catpuccino to go .
ID: 10294647 7. Hollywood girl and modern art nail stickers for instantly stylish digits. sokoglam.com
sokoglam.com
 Get the first sheet here and the second sheet here (both $8 from Soko Glam).
ID: 10275826 8. Plush bear claw gloves that will keep your hands warm while showing off your nails. View this image ›
amazon.com Double the compliments.
Get them from Amazon for $6.99 .
ID: 10275580 9. A pair of slip-ons with your favorite blubbery sea nuggets. View this image ›
bucketfeet.com You just call them manatees? Weird.
Get them from Bucket Feet for $75 .
ID: 10294439 10. A patterned elephant watch that’ll go with any outfit. View this image ›
amazon.com Get it from Amazon for $2.08 .
ID: 10274770 11. A fuzzy unicorn graphic backpack that you’ll want to pet for days. View this image ›
forever21.com And carry your stuff around in, but that comes second.
Get it from Forever 21 for $24.90 .
ID: 10292302 12. A scrumptious egg and toast breakfast for your finger. us.asos.com
us.asos.com
 Get it from Asos for $9.50 .
ID: 10306696 13. A cozy beanie that understands what is dearest to your heart. View this image ›
etsy.com Even if they don’t always think the same way back.
Get it from Katie Abey Design on Etsy for $12.48 .
ID: 10306648 14. Derpy earrings of Sanrio’s laziest egg in his natural habitat. View this image ›
modcloth.com Complaining and doing nothing.
Get them from Modcloth for $24.99 .
This fried-egg Gudetama crossbody bag from Think Geek is also super cute!
ID: 10294456 15. A gentle elephant that will comfort you during rough times ahead. View this image ›
amazon.com Get the necklace from Amazon for $10.99 . Also available in gold and silver.
ID: 10293713 16. A pair of adorable pandas who are just the best of friends. View this image ›
etsy.com You’ve got a friend in me
Get the pin from Xoxo Designs by Ruth on Etsy for $7.49 .
ID: 10281787 17. Soft pink socks for the ~sweetest~ monster around. View this image ›
amazon.com Get a pair from Amazon for $10.65 .
Also available in cat monster , coffee monster , and shoe monster versions.
ID: 10291729 18. And speaking of sweet, these earrings also fit the bill. View this image ›
forever21.com Get the set from Forever 21 for $3.90 .
ID: 10306246 19. A tiny vegan leather pouch that’s always ready to pucker up. urbanoutfitters.com
urbanoutfitters.com
 Lipstick addicts, where you at?
Get it from Urban Outfitters for $12 .
ID: 10306301 20. Multicolored fox socks that will make winter a little more bearable. View this image ›
amazon.com Get a 3-pack from Amazon for $11.99 .

modcloth.com
 Get them from Modcloth for $51.99 .

etsy.com Get the pin from Jesiiii on Etsy for $20 .

urbanoutfitters.com
Get it from Urban Outfitters for $16 .

Get it from La Cravette Du Chien on Etsy for $21.68 .

forever21.com
 Get it from Forever 21 for $17.90 .

shop.nylon.com And excellent signals.
Get the phone case from Nylon for $38 (iPhone 7). Also available for iPhone 6 , and as a portable charger .
ID: 10292515 27. Essential pins for any dedicated mermaid-in-training. View this image ›
modcloth.com Shoot for the seashells!
Get them from Modcloth for $16.99 .

shop.nylon.com
Get them from Nylon for $55 .

urbanoutfitters.com Get it from Urban Outfitters for $20 .

anthropologie.com Bow down to the ponytail queen.
Get them from Anthropologie for $18 .

iamfy.co
 So baby, know for sure that I’ll never let you go
Get it from Iamfy for $32 .
ID: 10275754 32. A charming origami dinosaur that’ll stomp its way into your heart. View this image ›
modcloth.com Get the necklace from Modcloth for $35 .
